<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<CustomField xmlns="http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata">
    <fullName>Status__c</fullName>
    <description>Lifecycle state. Open = newly auto-created and unresolved. In Progress = an assignee acknowledged it. Resolved = manually closed by a reviewer. Auto-Resolved = the underlying answer flipped from failing to passing, the trigger marked the finding closed but kept it for audit. Resolved-Exception = the tech (or admin) recorded an exception via the override workflow; unblocks submit but logs the reason for review. Waived = an admin explicitly waived the finding without remediation.</description>
